## 📚 Project Overview

This repository contains the complete implementation of the JPMorgan Chase Software Engineering Virtual Internship, including:

| Task | Description | Technologies |
|------|-------------|--------------|
| **Task 1** | Stock Price Data Feed Interface | Python, Sockets, Multi-threading |
| **Task 2** | Perspective Integration | TypeScript, Node.js, WebSocket |
| **Task 3** | Trading Dashboard | D3.js, TypeScript, Real-time viz |
| **Task 4** | Transaction System | Java, Spring Boot, Kafka |

